  "Description": {
    "English": "This peaceful space giant is a mutation of organism and starcraft, and can be tamed to swim through the stars alongside a fleet of frigates.<br><br>Recruiting this creature will add it to your frigate fleet. Manage your fleet from a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Fleet Command Room</span> aboard your freighter, and consult your <span class=\"name name-technology\">Navigator</span> to deploy frigates on lucrative expeditions.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "这个和平的太空巨人是有机体和飞船的变种，可以被驯服，并与护卫舰舰队一起在星辰中遨游。<br><br>招募这个生物将把它加入你的护卫舰舰队。在你货船上的<span class=\"name name-technology\">舰队指挥室</span> 管理你的舰队，并咨询你的<span class=\"name name-technology\">领航员</span>在有利可图的探险中部署你的护卫舰。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "這種愛好和平的太空巨物是生物和太空船的突變物，可以在馴服後，和巡防艦隊一起遨遊星海。<br><br>將此生物招募至你的巡防艦隊。登上貨船的<span class=\"name name-technology\">艦隊指揮處</span>管理你的艦隊，並徵詢<span class=\"name name-technology\">領航員</span>的意見，將巡防艦部署到有利可圖的探險中。"
  },
